# Never Seen TerpConnect in Your Life?

## No Idea How to Upload Your Homework?

Have no fear! By trial and error, I’ve found how to do that for my ENGL488A homework.

1.  Know your student log-in for UMD.
    (A space on TerpConnect is reserved for every student.)
    
2.  Open Komodo Edit 8. Go to **Edit ► Preferences**. 
    A pop-up opens asking for server info. 
    Fill it in like so, using your own Terp username and password.
 
3.  Open your [terpconnect.umd.edu](http://terpconnect.umd.edu). 
    Click on **File Manger** in the navigation bar. 
    You’ll see a giant button, **Access My Files**. Click it. 
    Fill in the blanks of the pop-up with your regular student log-in.
