        <figcaption>Here’s where you *would’ve* found the instructions to do this, 
                    if UMD would actually fix the broken links!
        </figcaption>
    </figure>

4.  Now you see almost all your server folders. 
    It automatically opens `home` for you, but you actually need to back up a bit. 
    Click on your student login, and a new list of folders will come up. 
    See `pub`? That stands for “public access”. 
    That’s where to upload files. 
    Close this. You’re down for now.
    
